{"prompt": "Create a portal for a local volunteer coordination platform. The site's branding should utilize a soft yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Volunteer Connect</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fffacd; /* Soft yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #ffd700; /* Slightly richer yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #f0e68c 3px solid; /* Khaki border */\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fffacd;\n        }\n        #main-content h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #daa520; /* Goldenrod */\n        }\n        .card {\n            background: #fff;\n            border: 1px solid #f0e68c;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #daa520;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #daa520;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: #b8860b; /* Darker goldenrod */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #ffd700;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Volunteer Connect</h1>\n            <p>Connecting passionate volunteers with local opportunities.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div id=\"main-content\" class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"intro\">\n            <h2>Welcome to Your Local Volunteering Hub</h2>\n            <p>Discover meaningful ways to give back to your community. Whether you have a few hours a week or want to get involved in a specific cause, Volunteer Connect makes it easy to find and sign up for opportunities that match your interests and availability.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"opportunities\">\n            <h2>Featured Opportunities</h2>\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <h3>Community Garden Help</h3>\n                <p>Assist with planting, weeding, and harvesting at the local community garden. Perfect for nature lovers!</p>\n                <button class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Sign Up</button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <h3>Animal Shelter Support</h3>\n                <p>Provide care and companionship to animals at the city's animal shelter. Walking dogs, cleaning, and socializing.</p>\n                <button class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Sign Up</button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <h3>Seniors' Activity Assistant</h3>\n                <p>Spend time with seniors at the local community center, helping with activities, games, and conversation.</p>\n                <button class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Sign Up</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"how-it-works\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n            <h2>How It Works</h2>\n            <p><strong>1. Browse:</strong> Explore a variety of volunteer roles posted by local organizations.</p>\n            <p><strong>2. Connect:</strong> Click to learn more about an opportunity and the organization behind it.</p>\n            <p><strong>3. Volunteer:</strong> Sign up directly through our platform and make a difference!</p>\n            <button class=\"cta-button\">Find More Opportunities</button>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Volunteer Connect. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}